hello all , I am an Indian and a banker by profession. I was born in a 
hindu family but don't believe in any religion. I am in  love with a 
Pakistani girl. I can't even express here how much i love her.  She came
 to india once and i met her in a symposium. We were in relationship 
since then. she left, after her work was done here. we used to talk a 
lot but when we confessed our love to our parents. MY parents were 
earlier angry with me but with time i convinced them. But when she told 
baout our relationship with her parents they threatened to lock her in 
room. I received a call from her brothers warning me that if i ever call
 her, they will behead me. I don't know what to do. IF she leaves me , i
 will die alone . And if  i try to contact her , her family or society 
might threaten her to kill . you tell me what should i do ? pls pls pls 
pls pls pls pls.
